    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\u2728 Wow \u2014 this one is the real deal! This vehicle is in absolutely mint condition, and it shows in every detail. The paint is flawless, gleaming like it just rolled off the showroom floor, and the interior is spotless \u2014 not a scratch, stain, or worn spot to be found. Under the hood, everything is in perfect mechanical order, running smooth and strong. If you've been searching for a used car that feels brand new, your search ends here. Don't miss your chance to own something truly special! \ud83c\udf1f",
      "price": 45000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in mint condition \u2014 a truly exceptional example that stands apart from typical used cars. The exterior is virtually flawless, showcasing paint that retains its original deep luster with no visible scratches, chips, or fading. Panel gaps are tight and uniform, and all chrome and trim pieces are pristine. The interior is equally impressive, with seats, carpeting, and dashboard surfaces showing no meaningful wear \u2014 it presents more like a showroom display than a pre-owned vehicle. Mechanically, the car runs and drives beautifully, with all systems functioning exactly as intended. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a used car that has been meticulously cared for and preserved, offering the next owner the pleasure of driving something that feels essentially new.",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in fair condition \u2014 buyers should come in with a clear and realistic understanding of what they're purchasing. The exterior shows noticeable wear including some paint fading, minor scratches, and small dents in a few areas, though the overall body structure remains intact and presentable. The interior has seen regular use and reflects its age, with some worn upholstery and minor scuffs on trim pieces, but it is clean and functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it would benefit from some attention \u2014 expect that routine maintenance and possibly a few repairs will be needed in the near term. This is a solid opportunity for a buyer who wants reliable transportation and is comfortable with a vehicle that has some miles and wear behind it, priced accordingly to reflect its honest, fair condition.",
      "price": 17000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 $20,000 - A solid everyday driver at a great value price! This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it runs reliably and gets you where you need to go, making it a practical choice for budget-conscious buyers. You'll notice some cosmetic wear and minor imperfections consistent with its age and use, and there may be a few small mechanical items worth attending to down the road. If you're looking for dependable transportation without the premium price tag, this could be the right fit for you! \ud83d\udd11",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition, and we're committed to giving you an honest and thorough picture of what you're purchasing. The exterior presents well \u2014 the paint retains most of its original luster with only minor surface scratches and light swirl marks consistent with regular use. There are no major dents or rust issues to report. The interior is clean and functional, with normal wear on the seats and trim that you'd expect from a well-used but well-maintained vehicle. Mechanically, the car runs reliably \u2014 the engine starts smoothly, transmission shifts properly, and all major systems are in good working order. There may be minor items that a detail-oriented buyer would want to address, but nothing that affects safety or day-to-day drivability. Overall, this is a solid, dependable vehicle that has been cared for and is ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
