      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Honest Deal for a Handy Buyer! This vehicle is priced to reflect its current poor condition \u2014 it has significant wear, mechanical issues, and will need attention before it's running at its best. That said, it's a real opportunity for a skilled DIYer, a parts hunter, or someone who loves a good project challenge. We're being fully upfront: this car needs work, and the price reflects exactly that. If you've got the skills and the vision, this could be your next great find!",
